summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of Lake Forest Park Second Addition, Country Home Plat Division Number 1, Section 32, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., Alderwood Acres, Madison Park Addition, Section 11, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M., Section 12, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M., Section 12, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M., and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
